L and R cannot go across each other, that is, their relative order in a string doesn't change.
Meanwhile, we should satisfy either one of cases below: 
```
case 1 : L = start[i] = end[j] and i >= j
case 2 : R = start[i] = end[j] and i <= j
```
for i, j are the index of next non-X character in start and end separately.

